the current and prospective labor requirements classified according to agricultural, industrial needs, including the number and type of workers needed, classified on an agricultural, industrial, occupational or regional basis; and

the current and prospective labor supply, including details as to the number, sex, skills, occupations, industries, areas of residence of the workers, and of the number, location, and characteristics of applicants for employment.

